race.comment: BLUER THAN BLUE (7) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 25.87 beating No More Extras. Ideally placed to take this out. SAINT TAY (1) turned spotting a big start finishing sixth (22.91) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Solid record here winning six races. Shapes as one to consider. LEKTRA JANE (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (25.98) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Worth following up. LEKTRA HOPPER (6) cannot be written off despite a miss here at his latest outing.
